Description.LocalizedString: A mixture of foul ichors gathered by the Observer.
A strange shape begins to take form inside the vial.
The sediments harden and twist into a familiar and horrifying shape.
Whatever was in here, it was unmistakably alive.
Whose idea was it to give drunk people sharp projectiles, anyway?
Did Jeff rescue the dog or did the dog rescue Jeff?
Of all his rugby awards, this is the one of which David is most proud.
An absolute terror on the pitch, David set records that may never be broken.
What’s better than a new album by your favorite band? Getting to design its album cover.
A typical high-school locker. Plus or minus a few weapons.
A doll from Charlotte’s childhood with its chest smashed, and a smaller doll representing Victor inserted.
Filled with attempts to come up with a Legion logo, but none of them came out quite right.
The pub David worked at. Carries fond memories of sticky floors and the smell of stale lager.
Anyone who hoped to get a positive visual on Susie after seeing this card will be sorely disappointed.
A magical place with treats so delicious they can only run it a few months a year.
Madeleine bought a porcelain doll and a toy soldier: one for if she had a girl, and one for a boy. The reality of the situation was far more complicated.
A regular noticed Jeff’s sketches and commissioned a mural at the abandoned lodge up Mount Ormond.
A book filled with sickening trials for witches  carried by those hunting Victor and Charlotte.
Nobody expected Charlotte and Victor to survive beyond infancy. This coffin remains unfilled.
As if this savory snack weren’t already perfect, they’ve been upgraded with maple-infused bacon.
The Entity will choke out all light, great and small.
Amber-colored syrup that makes any meal better. Or at least stickier.
A rare circumstance of birth led to a life of discrimination.
Without protection from maman, they lived their lives on the run.
Away from civilization, they struggled to survive.
Dreams of travelling to the new world gave them motivation to push on.
Nothing could tear them apart. Not even death.
His life was punctuated and defined by violence.
He felt the burden of expectations from family and fans.
Fearless in the face of a fight, a different confrontation terrified him.
Battered and bruised, he found the conviction to speak his truth.
He found within himself a new type of courage.
The only way forward is together!
